snippet.title: Zero Sievert - Official Early Access Release Date Update Trailer
snippet.description:
Explore the Universal Mall and fight against creepy enemies in this latest trailer for the upcoming top-down shooter game Zero Sievert.

Zero Sievert will be available in Early Access on November 15, 2022.

#GameTrailers #Gaming
